<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Saint James Harris Wood</strong></span> was on the road with his psychedelic punk blues band, the Saint James Catastrophe, when he picked up the heroin-smoking habit. This led to his imprisonment in a California high-desert penal colony, where he reinvented himself as a writer of the darkly absurd. Correspondence can be sent to: Saint James Harris Wood T30027 P.O. Box 4430 A1-217 Lancaster, CA 93539.</p><a href="/contributors/saint-james-harris-wood" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

